name: Killer Katrin / Ekaterina Novikova
description:
Ekaterina Novikova (also known as Killer Katrin, May 13, 1995) is a Lingerie model and a social influencer. Novikova is well-known for posting hot and bold photos on social media. She is also listed as one of the emerging models on Instagram.

If you like my work, a review is more than welcome! Also, follow me on Twitter or Instagram!

Looking for something... spicy? Here's my Patreon!

Also, I recently started a blog where I will gather resources and tutorials about my work here!

Hey nice people! Today I spoil you with something HOT. My textual inversion of Ekaterina Novikova, also known as Killer Katrin! I know that you'll like her ;) I used 40 public images of her with a 6600 steps process. To use it in your works:

  • warning: this textual inversion is nasty :D take a look at prompts in the gallery for inspiration;

  • download the file and place it into stable-diffusion-webui>embeddings folder;

  • add killer95 to your prompt;

  • keep the sampling steps around 20/25, and CFG between 7 and 8 to work well. Great results with DPM++ SDE Karras & Realistic Vision;
